<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Which category should the item be sorted into? Click on a category to choose it.</p>
<p class="tableblock">If the item should appear in multiple categories, just choose one of them for now. Once you’ve created the item, you can <a href="/en/item/managing-items#300">add the other categories too</a>.</p>
