<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Here you’ll see a list of the <a href="/en/item/settings/attributes">attributes</a> that you’ve already created in plentymarkets.</p>
<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Recommendation</em></strong>: It’s technically possible to select attributes here. However, we don’t recommend this.
